    "description_long": "This is a red pickup truck with a classic, boxy design and a single cab configuration. The front features a chrome grille and bumper, with rectangular headlights and side mirrors extending outward. The side profile reveals two doors and a long, open cargo bed with black trim, supported by four black wheels with silver hubcaps. The rear view shows a simple tailgate and a metallic bumper, with a license plate and taillights integrated into the design. The windows are tinted and the body panels have subtle reflections, indicating a smooth, glossy finish. The overall appearance suggests a utilitarian vehicle suitable for transporting goods or equipment in urban environments.",
